   "id": "80f88ec4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Task 1: Brain Tumor MRI Classification & Clustering\n",
    "\n",
    "**Module:** CCS3611 Machine Learning – Spring 2026\n",
    "\n",
    "**Dataset:** `BrainTumor.csv` – Pre-extracted statistical & textural features from MRI scans\n",
    "\n",
    "**Objectives:**\n",
    "1. Explore and understand the dataset (EDA)\n",
    "2. Select the most relevant features (correlation + information gain)\n",
    "3. Build and evaluate 3 classification models (Logistic Regression, Random Forest, XGBoost)\n",
    "4. Perform K-Means clustering to assess unsupervised grouping quality"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7f238ccf",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
