   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Phase 1 — Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)\n",
    "\n",
    "- Load the dataset and inspect its shape, data types, null values, and class balance\n",
    "- Plot feature distributions (histograms, boxplots) and their relationship with Class (violin plots)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "00f6418c",
