     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Keeping Dissimilarity (r = 0.7615 with Contrast ≤ 0.9)\n",
      "\n",
      "Dropped (collinearity): ['Variance', 'ASM']\n",
      "  • Variance dropped — mathematically redundant with Standard Deviation (Var = Std²)\n",
      "  • ASM dropped — mathematically redundant with Energy (Energy = √ASM)\n",
      "\n",
      "Remaining features (10): ['Mean', 'Standard Deviation', 'Entropy', 'Skewness', 'Kurtosis', 'Contrast', 'Energy', 'Homogeneity', 'Dissimilarity', 'Correlation']\n"
